## 🧪 QA & DoD

**Definition of Done (MVP UI)**

- Navbar/Footer, 5 pages stylisées, composants clés en place
- Dark mode + toggle, responsive 360→1440
- Focus states testés clavier
- Skeletons <100ms
- i18n prêt (FR/EN placeholders)
- Lighthouse ≥ 90 (Perf/Access/BP/SEO)

**Tests UX rapides**

- Timer: espace start/stop, inspection 15s visible
- Averages: avg5/avg12 corrects (DNF/+2 inclus)
- Filtres algos persistants
- Empty states clairs, erreurs explicites

